GHDL

GHDL is the tool to use, either in Windows, Mac or Linux: https://github.com/ghdl/ghdl/releases
There are binaries for all platforms in this github page.

GTKWave should be used to display the graphical output for the simulatios: https://gtkwave.sourceforge.net/
Can be installed as binary or compilied.
Dependencies for compilation:
TCL
TK
GCC++
GPerf
lzma-devel
libgtk2

